source.name: CTA - System Information - Developer Tool: Bus Tracker API
source.description: Data feeds which provide a pathway for developers to retrieve estimated arrival times, bus stop lists, route patterns, vehicle location information and more from the CTA Bus Tracker (SM) service and incorporate it into third-party apps and projects.
